title: The Osborne Brothers 1968-1974  [Bear Family 4 disc set]
description:
The Osborne Brothers 1968-1974  [Bear Family 4 disc set]


Picking up where Bear Family's previous box set left off, the four-disc set 1968-1974 contains all of the recordings the Osborne Brothers made for Decca Records during the late '60s and early '70s. Though the Osbornes were past their creative peak, they were experiencing a commercial revival during this era. Much of this music ranks among the duo's most enjoyable music, and any serious Osborne Brothers fan will need to invest in this excellent set. ~ Thom Owens
